Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:45.00,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}Death sickleが指揮者ね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:48.55,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}魅惑のレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.19,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}突き刺さる心の十字架に
